definitions.definition: An early station wagon or estate car in which the rear portion of the car's bodywork is made of wood, often associated with Southern California surfing culture.
A wooden rollercoaster; an amusement ride whose rails are overlaid upon a wooden track.
Made of wood, or having wood-like properties.

definitions.example: Subshrubs, shrubs, trees and lianas are all woody plants.
the woody parts of a plant
